item.title: About der Reineke
item.description: Hello there My name is Reineke Fuchs, for those who missed it. I am a student(still) currently working on a post-degree certificate in Cybersecurity; my Bachelors is in the Humanities. I went to grad school for a little bit for Germanic Studies, but I hated it so I dropped out. I then started teaching myself how to program in Python, as well as learned some Data Analysis. I am currently building my knowledge base in Data Science and Cybersecurity.
